text: Heinke is the name of: * Heinke (diving equipment makers) (1818–1869), in London (England), a series of companies run by various members of a Heinke family * George Henry Heinke (1882–1940), Nebraska Republican politician * Sarah Kathleen Heinke (born 1990), American voice actress * Heinke van der Merwe (born 1985, Johannesburg), professional South African rugby player * Harald Heinke (born 1955), German Olympic judoka == See also == * Heincke Category:Dutch masculine given names Category:Low German surnames
title: Heinke
